*'''★ How To Play''':
**You score points when '''[[Warspite]]''' hits against the '''"Coin Manjuu"''' [[File:Coin Manjuu.png|25px|]]
**Hitting two or more '''"Coin Manjuu"''' [[File:Coin Manjuu.png|25px|]] in a row will increase your '''"Combo Counter"''' and the points you gain from '''"Coin Manjuu"'''. The most points you can gain from '''"Coin Manjuu"''' is '''3 points'''.
**Hitting a '''"Firecracker Manjuu"''' [[File:Firecracker Manjuu.png|25px|]] will reset your '''"Combo Counter" to 0'''.
**If you complete the mini-game with '''10 points or more''', you will gain '''1 [[File:Royal_Emblem.png|25px|]] "Service Medal"  and 1 [[File:Dice.png|30px|link=]] "Dice"'''.<br>'''➤''' The maximum number of '''[[File:Royal_Emblem.png|25px|]] "Service Medals"''' you can obtain starts at 1 on January 31st and will be increased by one daily until February 6th (7 total).<br>'''➤''' The maximum number of '''[[File:Dice.png|30px|link=]] "Dice"''' you can obtain starts at 1 on January 31st and will be increased by one daily until February 14th (15 total).<br>'''➤''' Furthermore, obtaining a '''[[File:Dice.png|30px|link=]] "Dice"''', will be used in the event '''[[Lunar_New_Year_2019#Spring_Festival_Board_Game|"Spring Festival Board Game"]]''' after clearing the mini-game.<br>'''➤ Note: [[File:Dice.png|30px|link=]] "Dice" are NOT rewarded for the EN run of the event.'''

